\begin_layout Standard
On the other hand, the canonical CNF 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
(\neg A\ali\neg B\ali C)\inn(\neg A\ali B\ali\neg C)\inn(\neg A\ali B\ali C)\inn(A\ali\neg B\ali C)
\]

\end_inset

corresponds to circuit 
\begin_inset Float figure
placement h
wide false
