\begin_layout Standard
Let a set 
\begin_inset Formula $S$
\end_inset

 be partially ordered with relation 
\begin_inset Formula $R$
\end_inset

 and let 
\begin_inset Formula $U\subseteq S$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
If there exists 
\begin_inset Formula $a\in S$
\end_inset

 such that for all 
\begin_inset Formula $x\in U$
\end_inset

