 is below 
\begin_inset Formula $y$
\end_inset

 
\begin_inset Formula $\cee$
\end_inset

 
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

 is a special case of 
\begin_inset Formula $y$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

