\end_layout

\end_inset

.
 This is such a number 
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

 from the set with which every other number 
\begin_inset Formula $y$
\end_inset

 is in relation 
\begin_inset Formula $y<x$
\end_inset

.
